channel.title: GoBabyGo Gilford NH
channel.description: The Introduction to Engineering class at Gilford High School built their first 2 cars during spring 2019 for 3 students at our local elementary school. Since then, we've received a donation from an anonymous donor to continue buying 1-2 cars each year for the foreseeable future. Looks like we're in the GBG business! Keep up the great work, everyone!
